---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Summary">
    <section class="py-20">
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">IT 11 Unit Summary</h2>
			<p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">IT 11 talks about the past, the present, and the future of ICT. It consisted of 7 units, here are the summary for each unit.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
			<div class="bg-tech-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-tech-accent transition-colors group">
				<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-tech-accent transition-colors">
					<svg  width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M14.5 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7.5L14.5 2z" />
                        <path d="M14 2v6h6" />
                        <circle cx="8" cy="18" r="4" />
                        <path d="M8 14v2.5l1.5 1.5" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Introduction to ICT</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
					This unit tackled an overview on ICT. Also it explored the history of Technology from big computers like UNIVAC to smaller ones like smartphones.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-tech-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-tech-accent transition-colors group">
				<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-tech-accent transition-colors">
					<!-- Lock SVG Icon -->
					<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
  <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="15" rx="2" ry="2"/>
  <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/>
  <line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12" y2="21"/>
</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Computers in our Daily Life</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
					This unit discussed the different types of computers and their uses in our daily lives, from personal computers to embedded systems. It also where students learned that 1+1=10. Furthermore, flowcharts and algorithms were introduced here.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-tech-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-tech-accent transition-colors group">
				<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-tech-accent transition-colors">
					<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path 
    d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12C2 17.52 6.48 22 12 22C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12C22 6.48 17.52 2 12 2ZM2 12H22M12 2C14.5 2 16.5 6.5 16.5 12C16.5 17.5 14.5 22 12 22C9.5 22 7.5 17.5 7.5 12C7.5 6.5 9.5 2 12 2ZM12 2V22M2.6 16.5H21.4M2.6 7.5H21.4" 
    stroke="currentcolor" 
    stroke-width="2" 
    stroke-linecap="round" 
    stroke-linejoin="round"
  />
</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">The internet and World Wide Web</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
					This unit discussed the history and evolution of the internet and the World Wide Web. It covered topics such as web browsers, search engines, and online communication tools. It also gave tips and tricks for safe and effective internet use.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-tech-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-tech-accent transition-colors group">
				<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-tech-accent transition-colors">
					<!-- Code SVG Icon -->
					<svg viewBox="-3 -3 30 30" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path 
    d="M12 15C13.6569 15 15 13.6569 15 12C15 10.3431 13.6569 9 12 9C10.3431 9 9 10.3431 9 12C9 13.6569 10.3431 15 12 15ZM12 9V7M9.5 10.5L8 9M14.5 10.5L16 9M12 15V17M9.5 13.5L8 15M14.5 13.5L16 15M19.07 4.93C20.94 6.8 22 9.32 22 12C22 17.52 17.52 22 12 22C6.48 22 2 17.52 2 12C2 6.48 6.48 2 12 2C13.36 2 14.66 2.27 15.85 2.77M17 7C17 7 18 8 19 8C20 8 21 7 21 7M19 8V11C19 12.5 18 14 17 15M16.5 4.5C16.5 4.5 17.5 5.5 18.5 5.5C19.5 5.5 20.5 4.5 20.5 4.5" 
    stroke="currentColor" 
    stroke-width="1.5" 
    stroke-linecap="round" 
    stroke-linejoin="round"
  />
</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Information, Control, Ethics</h3>

				<p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
					This unit focused on the ethical use of information and communication technology. Topics included data privacy, digital citizenship, and the societal impact of technology. It also introduced different laws and regulations related to ICT in the Philippines.
				</p>
			</div>
            
            <div class="bg-tech-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-tech-accent transition-colors group">
				<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-tech-accent transition-colors">
					<!-- Lock SVG Icon -->
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path 
    d="M12 9.5C13.3807 9.5 14.5 8.38071 14.5 7C14.5 5.61929 13.3807 4.5 12 4.5C10.6193 4.5 9.5 5.61929 9.5 7C9.5 8.38071 10.6193 9.5 12 9.5ZM12 12C9.24 12 7 14.24 7 17V21H17V17C17 14.24 14.76 12 12 12ZM5 12.5C6.38071 12.5 7.5 11.3807 7.5 10C7.5 8.61929 6.38071 7.5 5 7.5C3.61929 7.5 2.5 8.61929 2.5 10C2.5 11.3807 3.61929 12.5 5 12.5ZM2 21V19C2 17.1 3.1 15.5 4.7 14.6ZM19 12.5C20.3807 12.5 21.5 11.3807 21.5 10C21.5 8.61929 20.3807 7.5 19 7.5C17.6193 7.5 16.5 8.61929 16.5 10C16.5 11.3807 17.6193 12.5 19 12.5ZM22 21V19C22 17.1 20.9 15.5 19.3 14.6" 
    stroke="currentColor" 
    stroke-width="1.5" 
    stroke-linecap="round" 
    stroke-linejoin="round"
  />
</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Culture and Society</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
					This unit explored the impact of technology on culture and society. It started with definitions of literacy then progressed to different types of literacies in ICT such as digital literacy, media literacy, and information literacy. It also discussed the role of technology in shaping cultural norms and values.
				</p>
			</div>
            <div class="bg-tech-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-tech-accent transition-colors group">
				<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-tech-accent transition-colors">
					<!-- Lock SVG Icon -->
					<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
    <path
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
        stroke-width="2"
        d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.856-1.487M15 10a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 0a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM5 20a3 3 0 015.856-1.487M5 10a2 2 0 110-4 2 2 0 010 4z"
    />
</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Design Principles</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
					This unit covered the fundamental principles of design in technology, including usability, accessibility, and user experience. It emphasized the importance of creating intuitive and inclusive digital products. it also included branding which tackled logo design, color theory, and typography.
				</p>
			</div>
            <div class="bg-tech-surface p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-tech-accent transition-colors group">
				<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-tech-accent transition-colors">
					<!-- Lock SVG Icon -->
					<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
							stroke-width="2"
							d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"
						/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Trends, Issues, and Challenges</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
					This unit examined current trends, issues, and challenges in the field of ICT. Topics included emerging technologies, cybersecurity threats, and the digital divide. This was supposed to be a separate unit but was merged with Unit 6 due to time constraints and how similar the topics were.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
